### Refactored (no-fallback applied)
- `decompress_gzip_to_vec`: BGZF/multi-member errors propagate directly
- `decompress_gzip_libdeflate`: deterministic routing, no cascading
- `decompress_single_member`: parallel gated on `isal_decompress::is_available()` (x86_64 only)
